jyhVw prmwqmw (su`D) sony vrgI pivqR hsqI vwlw hY, jo inrw cwnx hI cwnx hY,
ijs vrgw hor koeI nhIN hY, jo iqMnW BvnW dw mwlk hY,
ieh swrw Awkwr ijs dw (srgux) srUp hY, aus prmwqmw dw sdw-iQr qy kdy nwh mu`kx vwlw nwm-Dn mYnUM (gurU-srw& qoN) imilAw hY ]4]
jo prmwqmw pMjW q`qW ivc, mwieAw dy iqMn guxW ivc, nO KMfW ivc Aqy cwr kUtW ivc ivAwpk hY,
jo DrqI qy AwkwS nUM AwpxI s`iqAw dy Awsry (QW isr) itkweI rKdw hY;
gurU-srw& mnu`K dy bwhr id`sdy Awkwr vl dOVdy mn nUM aus prmwqmw vl prqw ky ilAwauNdw hY ]5]
(gurU-srw& d`sdw hY ik prmwqmw swrI isRStI ivc rimAw hoieAw hY, pr) auh mnu`K mUrK hY ijs nUM A`KW nwl (pRBU) nhIN id`sdw,
ijs dI jIB ivc (pRBU dw) nwm-rs nhIN AwieAw, jo gurU dy d`sy aupdyS nUM nhIN smJdw[
auh mnu`K ivhulI mwieAw ivc msq ho ky jgq nwl JgVy shyVdw hY ]6]
gurU dI sRySt sMgq dI brkiq nwl mnu`K sRySt jIvn vwlw bx jWdw hY,
Awqmk guxW dI pRwpqI leI dOV-B`j krdw hY qy (Awpxy AMdroN nwm-AMimRq dI shwieqw nwl) AOgux Do dyNdw hY[
(ieh g`l XkInI hY ik) gurU dI d`sI syvw krn qoN ibnw (AOguxW qoN ^lwsI nhIN huMdI, qy) Afol Awqmk AvsQw nhIN imldI ]7]
pRBU nwm kImqI hIry qy lwlW dy vWg hY,
jo moqI (vrgy su`cw) mn vwly mnu`K dI rws-pUMjI bx jWdw hY[
hy nwnk! gurU-srw& ijs mnu`K nUM myhr dI nzr nwl vyKdw hY auh inhwl ho jWdw hY ]8]5]
rwg Awsw iv`c gurU nwnkdyv jI dI bwxI[
(hy mnu`K! qUM) gurU dy snmuK ho ky Awpxy mn ivc prmwqmw nwl fUMGI sWJ pw Aqy prmwqmw ivc juVI surq (dw AwnMd) mwx,
gurU dI srn pY ky qUM Awpxy AMdr pRBU dw itkwxw pCwx[
gurU dy snmuK rih ky qUM gurU dy Sbd nUM Awpxy soc-mMfl ivc itkw, (ieh qyry jIvn-s&r leI) rwhdwrI hY ]1]
ies qrHW pRBU-crnW nwl pRym Aqy prmwqmw dI BgqI kr ky auh au~cI ivcwr dw mwlk bx jWdw hY[
gurU dy snmuK rihx vwly mnu`K nUM prmwqmw dw sdw-iQr rihx vwlw nwm pRwpq ho jWdw hY ]1] rhwau]
(jo mnu`K gurU dy snmuK rihMdw hY auh) idn rwq Awpxy ihrdy-QW ivc prmwqmw dw pivqR sRySt fyrw bxweI r`Kdw hY,
iqMnW BvnW ivc ivAwpk qy vwSnw-rihq pRBU nwl aus dI fUMGI sWJ pY jWdI hY[
(qUM BI) ABu`l gurU qoN (Bwv, srn pY ky) prmwqmw dI rzw nUM smJ ]2]
(jyhVw mnu`K gurU dI srn pYNdw hY aus dy) AMdr itkvW AwnMd bixAw rihMdw hY, aus nUM kdy koeI icMqw nhIN poNhdI;
prmwqmw dw Awqmk jIvn dyx vwlw sRySt rs vwlw nwm qy prmwqmw nwl fUMGI sWJ aus mnu`K dw Awqmk Bojn bx jWdw hY[
(jy gurU dI srn pY ky) jgq kwmwidk pMjW nUM mukw dyvy qW swrw jgq hI suKI ho jwey ]3]
(gurU dy snmuK rihx vwlw mnu`K ieauN Ardws krdw hY: hy pRBU!) swrI isRStI ivc qyrI hI joiq (pRkwS kr rhI hY), qy hryk jIv qyrw hI pYdw kIqw hoieAw hY[
prmwqmw Awp hI jIvW dy sMjog bxWdw hY, qy Awp hI iPr ivCoVw pw dyNdw hY[
jo kuJ krqwr Awp hI krdw hY auhI huMdw hY ]4]
prmwqmw Awp hI isRStI nUM Fwh ky Awp hI muV auswrdw hY, aus dy hukm Anuswr hI jgq muV aus ivc lIn ho jWdw hY[
jo aus nUM cMgw lgdw hY aus Anuswr aus dw hukm c`ldw hY[
gurU dI srn Awaux qoN ibnw koeI jIv pUrn prmwqmw nUM pRwpq nhIN kr skdw ]5]
ijs pRwxI dI surq bcpn jW buFypy iv`c (qy nwh hI jvwnI smy) kdy BI prmwqmw ivc nhIN juVdI,
(sgoN) Br-jvwnI ivc auh (jvwnI dy) AhMkwr ivc fu`bw rihMdw hY,
auh prmwqmw dy nwm qoN KuMJ ky Aw^r (ieQoN) kIh K`tygw? ]6]
ijs prmwqmw dw id`qw AMn qy Dn jIv vrqdw rihMdw hY, jy Afol AvsQw ivc itk ky aus nwl kdy BI sWJ BI nhIN pWdw,
qy mwieAw dI Btkxw ivc jIvn-rwh qoN KuMiJAw rihMdw hY, qW Aw^r pCqWdw hY[
aus dy gl ivc moh dI PwhI peI rihMdI hY, moh ivc hI auh sdw J`lw hoieAw iPrdw hY ]7]
auh jgq nUM (moh ivc) fu`bdw vyK ky (moh qoN) fr ky B`j jWdy hn,
auh bVy BwgW vwly hn qy siqgurU ny auhnW nUM (moh dI kYd qoN) bcw ilAw hY,
jyhVy mnu`K gurU dI crnIN l`gdy (Srn pYNdy) hn, hy nwnwk! ]8]6]
rwg Awsw iv`c gurU nwnkdyv jI dI bwxI[
jyhVy mnu`K (dUijAW nUM hI suxwx vwsqy BgqI dy) gIq gWdy hn, pr auhnW dy ic`q ivc mMdy ^iAwl (mOjUd) hn;
jyhVy (hornW nUM) rwg (dRvYK qoN bcx dIAW g`lW) suxw ky AKvWdy hn ik AsIN rwg dRvYK qoN bcy hoey hW,
prmwqmw dw nwm ismrn qoN ibnw auhnW dy mn ivc JUT (v`sdw) hY, auhnW dy mn ivc kukrm (itky hoey) hn ]1]
(hornW nUM m`qW dyx vwly) hy mn! qUM (kukrmW ivc) ikauN Btk irhw hYN? Awpxy AMdr hI itikAw rhu[
jyhVy mnu`K gurU dy snmuK huMdy hn auh prmwqmw dy nwm ivc juV ky (ivkwrW vloN) ht jWdy hn[ hy mn! qUM BI gurU dI rwhIN Bwl kr ky shj AvsQw ivc itk ky prmwqmw nUM l`B leyNgw ]1] rhwau]
ijs mnu`K dy mn ivc srIr ivc kwm hY kRoD hY moh hY,
ijs dy AMdr l`b hY loB hY AhMkwr hY, (ijs dy AMdr iehnW ivkwrW dw) klyS hY,
prmwqmw dw nwm ismrn qoN ibnw aus dw mn (iehnW dw twkrw krn dw) ikvyN hOslw kr skdw hY? ]2]
jyhVw mnu`K Awpxy AMdr sdw-iQr pRBU nwl sWJ pw lYNdw hY, auh Awpxy Awqmw ivc (qIrQ-) ieSnwn kr irhw hY,
AYsw mnu`K (gurU dI srn pY ky) AwpxI AMdrlI Awqmk hwlq smJ lYNdw hY[
(pr gurU dy) s`cy Sbd qoN ibnw prmwqmw dw itkwxw koeI mnu`K nhIN pCwx skdw ]3]
jyhVw mnu`K id`sdy sMswr nUM AidRSt pRBU ivc lIn kr lYNdw hY (Bwv, AwpxI bRirqI nUM bwhr vloN rok ky AMdr lY AwauNdw hY;)
ijs pRBU dI s`iqAw-igxqI imxqI qoN pry hY aus sdw-iQr pRBU nUM jyhVw mnu`K ismrn dI rwhIN Awpxy ihrdy ivc itkWdw hY,
auh mnu`K jnm mrn dy gyV ivc nhIN AwauNdw ]4]
